<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Sunil Chhetri - Indian Football Star</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css">
    <style>
        /* Professional CSS style for the title */
        .title {
            font-size: 2.5rem; /* Adjust font size as needed */
            color: #333; /* Dark text color */
            text-align: center; /* Center align the text */
            margin-top: 80px; /* Add space below the title */
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif; /* Use a clean sans-serif font */
            font-weight: bold; /* Make the title bold */
        }

        /* Style for footballer details */
        .footballer-details {
            margin: 30px auto; /* Center the footballer details */
            max-width: 600px; /* Limit width to improve readability */
            padding: 20px; /* Add padding for better visual appearance */
            background-color: #fff; /* White background color for footballer details */
            border-radius: 10px; /* Add rounded corners */
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); /* Add shadow for depth */
        }

        /* Style for footballer image */
        .footballer-image {
            width: 100%; /* Ensure the image fills the container */
            border-radius: 10px; /* Add rounded corners */
            margin-bottom: 20px; /* Add space below the image */
        }

        /* Style for footballer name */
        .footballer-name {
            font-size: 1.8rem; /* Adjust font size for footballer name */
            color: #333; /* Dark text color */
            margin-bottom: 10px; /* Add space below the footballer name */
        }

        /* Style for footballer bio */
        .footballer-bio {
            font-size: 1.2rem; /* Adjust font size for footballer bio */
            color: #666; /* Dark gray text color */
            line-height: 1.5; /* Set line height for better readability */
            margin-bottom: 20px; /* Add space below the footballer bio */
        }

        /* Apply linear gradient background */
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f5f5, #e0e0e0); /* Light grey gradient colors */
            min-height: 100vh; /* Set minimum height to cover the viewport */
            display: flex; /* Use flexbox for vertical centering */
            flex-direction: column; /* Stack child elements vertically */
            justify-content: center; /* Center content horizontally */
            align-items: center; /* Center content vertically */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Include header partial with navbar -->
    <% include partials/header %>

    <!-- Main content for Sunil Chhetri page -->
    <div class="container">
        <div class="footballer-details">
            <img class="footballer-image" src="/images/image4.jpeg" alt="Sunil Chhetri">
            <h2 class="footballer-name">Sunil Chhetri</h2>
            <p class="footballer-bio">
                Sunil Chhetri is an Indian professional footballer widely regarded as one of the greatest players in the history of Indian football. Born on August 3, 1984, in Secunderabad, India, Chhetri has had a remarkable career both at the national and club levels.
                <br><br>
                Chhetri currently serves as the captain of the Indian national football team and has been instrumental in leading the team to numerous victories and accolades. He is the all-time leading goal scorer for the Indian national team, with a prolific scoring record.
                <br><br>
                At the club level, Chhetri has played for various teams in India as well as abroad. He has been a key player for Bengaluru FC in the Indian Super League (ISL) and has achieved significant success with the club, winning league titles and other prestigious tournaments.
                <br><br>
                Throughout his career, Chhetri has been recognized for his exceptional skills, leadership qualities, and dedication to the sport. He has received numerous awards and honors, including the Padma Shri, India's fourth-highest civilian award, for his contributions to Indian football.
                <br><br>
                Off the field, Chhetri is known for his philanthropic work and efforts to promote football in India. He continues to inspire aspiring footballers across the country and remains a beloved figure in Indian sports.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Include footer partial -->
    <% include partials/footer %>
</body>
</html>
